80
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:53,560
Ibu.

81
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,890
Bukankah aku sudah memberitahumu?

82
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,310
Menurut adat istiadat,

83
