00:41:18,230 --> 00:41:19,190
Yang Mulia, lepaskan!

967
00:41:19,190 --> 00:41:20,150
Suige, lepaskan!

968
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:21,210
Apa yang sedang terjadi?

969
00:41:22,230 --> 00:41:23,000
